      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Once the mushrooms have started to caramelise, add the<strong> spinach</strong> and your <strong>soy sauce</strong> to the pan and cook for 2-3 min or until starting to wilt</p>",
